OL,3,CBoy, 14, charged with murder of 80-
OL,4,Cyear-old dog walker
OL,6,FPolice have charged a 14-year-old boy
OL,7,Fwith murder, after the death of dog
OL,8,Fwalker Bhim Kohli in a Leicestershire
OL,9,Fpark.
OL,11,FThe 80-year-old was attacked on Sunday
OL,12,Fnight (1 September) in Franklin Park.
OL,13,FHe was taken to hospital in a critical
OL,14,Fcondition, but later died.
OL,16,FA post-mortem examination showed he
OL,17,Fdied as a result of a neck injury,
OL,18,Fpending further tests.
