OL,3,CBoy, 14, charged with murder of 80-
OL,4,Cyear-old dog walker
OL,6,FThe attack happened at around 6.30pm,
OL,7,Fclose to the park entrance in Bramble
OL,8,FWay.
OL,10,FFive children were originally arrested
OL,11,Fon suspicion of murder but four were
OL,12,Flater released without charge.
OL,14,FThe 14-year-old is due to appear at
OL,15,FLeicester Magistrate's Court on
OL,16,FThursday morning.
