OL,3,CBoy, 14, charged with murder of 80-
OL,4,Cyear-old dog walker
OL,6,FBecause Leicestershire Police had
OL,7,Fprevious contact with Mr Kohli the
OL,8,Fforce made a voluntary referral to the
OL,9,FIndependent Office of Police Conduct
OL,10,F(IOPC). Following further contact with
OL,11,Fthe IOPC, the force has now made a
OL,12,Fmandatory referral.
OL,14,FAndrew Baxter, deputy chief crown
OL,15,Fprosecutor for the Crown Prosecution
OL,16,FService, said: "The Crown Prosecution
OL,17,FService has reviewed a file of
OL,18,Fevidence from Leicestershire Police
OL,19,Fand has authorised a charge of murder
OL,20,Fagainst a 14-year-old boy in relation
OL,21,Fto the death of Bhim Sen Kohli.
